#AI Impact
AI in Fraud Detection and Risk Management
## 2. How AI Works in Fraud Detection
•⁠  ⁠**Anomaly Detection**: AI identifies behaviors that deviate from the norm (e.g., sudden large withdrawals).
•⁠  ⁠**Pattern Recognition**: ML algorithms learn from historical fraud cases and spot similar trends.
## 3. How AI Supports Risk Management
•⁠  ⁠**Predictive Analytics**: AI predicts risks based on historical and real-time data.
•⁠  ⁠**Risk Scoring**: Customers and transactions are scored for risk, helping companies prioritize reviews.
